history.content:
Hi everyone,

When I tried to enroll in EE290C-003, the SOC design course, I got an error saying that I needed instructor permission to enroll in the class. However, Professor Kris Pister is on sabbatical this semester, according to his website. Resultantly, who would I need to contact to get permission to enroll in this course?

EDIT: nvmd, resolved
